@PresentationLayer_HostAddress = http://localhost:5122
@AccessToken = paste-access-token-here

### FE Swagger/testing guide
GET {{PresentationLayer_HostAddress}}/api/test-support/swagger-guide
Accept: application/json

### Local test accounts
GET {{PresentationLayer_HostAddress}}/api/test-support/test-accounts
Accept: application/json

### Login: moderator for account management
POST {{PresentationLayer_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "test.training",
  "password": "Test@123456"
}

### Login: lecturer
POST {{PresentationLayer_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "test.lecturer",
  "password": "Test@123456"
}

### Login: legacy local admin
POST {{PresentationLayer_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "12345"
}

###

### Bootstrap first admin: Development only and only when users table is empty
POST {{PresentationLayer_HostAddress}}/api/auth/bootstrap-admin
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin@cpms.local",
  "password": "123456"
}

###

### List accounts
GET {{PresentationLayer_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Create lecturer without department
POST {{PresentationLayer_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": null,
  "identityCode": "SE194673",
  "email": "gv001@cpms.local",
  "password": "Test@123456",
  "role": "Lecturer",
  "fullName": "Duong Thanh Thanh Duy",
  "department": null,
  "position": null,
  "permissionScope": null,
  "isPartTime": false,
  "classCode": null,
  "batch": null,
  "major": null
}

### Create evaluation panel account
POST {{PresentationLayer_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": null,
  "identityCode": "PN001",
  "email": "panel001@cpms.local",
  "password": "Test@123456",
  "role": "EvaluationPanel",
  "fullName": "Nguyen Van Panel",
  "department": "Software Engineering",
  "position": null,
  "permissionScope": null,
