### Save lecturer weekly availability
PUT {{PresentationLayer_HostAddress}}/api/review-availability/week?semesterId=1&weekStart=2026-06-15
Authorization: Bearer {{AccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "slots": [
    { "dayOfWeek": 1, "slot": 1 },
    { "dayOfWeek": 3, "slot": 2 }
  ]
}
